PC PC_SayLoveuHateu@SayLoveuHateu
process SayLoveuHateu@OpLoveuHateu
operator OpLoveuHateu.Interleave
import SayAtLeastOnce as SayLonceI for PC_SayAtLeastOnce
reference RefLoveu:SayAtLeastOnce[something/loveu]
ref_connector RefLoveu->SayLonceI
op_connector OpLoveuHateu->RefLoveu
reference RefHateu:SayAtLeastOnce[something/hateu]
ref_connector RefHateu->SayLonceI
op_connector OpLoveuHateu->RefHateu
